md:
giải nghĩa từ "branch" sang tiếng việt; đưa ra nghĩa tiếng việt theo từ loại và đưa ra câu ví dụ, các từ liên quan.

* branch (noun) - nhánh, chi nhánh
	+ Meaning: a part of a tree that grows out from the trunk or a main branch
	+ Example: The branch of the tree broke off in the storm.
	+ Related words: tree, trunk, leaf, root
* branch (verb) - phân nhánh, chia nhánh
	+ Meaning: to divide or separate into different parts or groups
	+ Example: The company branched out into new markets.
	+ Related words: divide, separate, split, expand
* branch (noun) - ngành, lĩnh vực
	+ Meaning: a specialized area of study or work
	+ Example: She studied the branch of physics that deals with the behavior of atoms.
	+ Related words: field, area, discipline, specialty

Note: The meaning of "branch" can vary depending on the context in which it is used.
